BASKETBALL ROUNDUP; CLU WARMS UP IN SECOND HALF, REMAINS PERFECT WITH 90-63 WIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cal Lutheran turned an 11-point game into a blowout by shooting 66% after the 
intermission to fuel a 90-63 victory over Whittier on Wednesday night in a 
Southern California Intercollegiate Athletic Conference game. 
</P>
<P>
