<P>
 The price is $65 for the four-course meal, which includes a goat cheese salad, 
a cheese souffle and wine. 
</P>
<P>
 Among the chefs attending will be Jean Pierre Lemanissier of Restaurant 
Antoine and Christian Rassinoux of the Ritz-Carlton. 
</P>
<P>
