 * Los Angeles Archdiocese 
</P>
<P>
 Decisions to close will be made on a school-by-school basis for elementary. 
All high schools open except Alemany, Mission Hills, St. Genevieve's, Panorama 
City. 
</P>
<P>
 * Adat Ari El 
</P>
<P>
 This private school in North Hollywood will be closed today. For information, 
call 818-766-4992. 
</P>
<P>
 * Landmark West School, Encino 
</P>
<P>
 This school for the learning disabled will be closed through Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Meadow Oaks School 
</P>
<P>
 This private school in Calabasas will be closed today and Friday. Classes will 
resume Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Newhall School District 
</P>
<P>
 All schools closed today and Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Pilgrim School 
</P>
