 This private school at 540 S. Commonwealth Ave. will be closed today. 
</P>
<P>
 * Santa Monica-Malibu Unified School District 
</P>
<P>
 Roosevelt Elementary, Lincoln Middle School, Santa Monica High School, Olympic 
High School, John Muir, SMASH and Ocean Park Childrens Center will be closed 
today. 
</P>
<P>
 * Seeds University Elementary School 
</P>
<P>
 This school on the UCLA campus will be open today. 
