 * Holy Cross Medical Center, Mission Hills * Kaiser Permanente: 
</P>
<P>
 Services previously provided in Granada Hills have been transferred to the 
Woodland Hills facility. Regularly scheduled appointments will continue today. 
Mail Pickup 
</P>
<P>
 Mail will not be delivered today to homes in Zip Codes 91311, 91331, 91343, 
91344 and 91345. 
</P>
<P>
 Residents may pick up their mail beginning at 10 a.m. at these local post 
offices: 
</P>
<P>
 * 91311: Chatsworth Post Office, 21606 Devonshire St. * 91331: Arleta Branch, 
9454 Arleta Ave. * 91343: North Hills Post Office, 8759 Sepulveda Blvd. * 91344 
and 91345: Mission City Annex Post Office, 1091 Sepulveda Blvd., Mission Hills. 
</P>
<P>
 * Call (818) 757-2100 for further information. 
</P>
<P>
 These branches are closed today: 
</P>
<P>
 * Village Post Office, 11000 Wilshire Blvd, Los Angeles. * Eden Post Office, 
1525 N. Alvarado St., Los Angeles. Donations 
</P>
<P>
 * Blood donations: 
</P>
<P>
 Donating blood takes about an hour. Persons wishing to donate should be at 
least 18 years old, weigh more than 110 pounds and be in good health. For blood 
donation sites: 
</P>
<P>
 * American Red Cross (800) 974-2113 
</P>
<P>
 Blood donations can be made from 9 a.m. to 6 p.m. today at this location: 
</P>
<P>
 * Antelope Valley Hospital Medical Center Blood Donor Center 
</P>
<P>
 1600 West Ave. J 
</P>
<P>
 Lancaster 
</P>
<P>
 (805) 949-5622 
</P>
