<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARTHQUAKE: THE LONG ROAD BACK; COSTLY QUAKES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Gov. Pete Wilson says the financial toll from Monday's earthquake could 
"conservatively" rise to $30 billion or more.By comparison, the 10 most costly 
earthquakes in U.S. history, in estimated property damage: 04,20,06,11,19 
EARTHQUAKE YEAR MAGNITUDE AMOUNT (MILLIONS) Loma Prieta 1989 7.1 $590 Sylmar 
