<HEADLINE>
<P>
IN HOG HEAVEN WITH HARLEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LAURIE K. SCHENDEN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Motorcycle lovers will be in hog heaven at the Miller Genuine Draft Motorcycle 
Swap Meet: Harley-Davidson -- the king of bikes -- will be the featured 
manufacturer at the swap series. 
</P>
<P>
 One area designated for motorcycle sales features vintage and custom bikes. 
There are also hundreds of shiny new and used parts for dirt bikes, cafe racers 
and daily riders, plus accessories from helmets to saddlebags to handlebars, 
clothing from traditional leather jackets to gloves and bike-related 
memorabilia. 
</P>
<P>
 The swap meet takes place Friday from 5-10 p.m. at Orange County Fairgrounds, 
88 Fair Drive, Costa Mesa. Admission is $6; children under 12 free; parking is 
free. For information, call (714) 364-2542. LAURIE K. SCHENDEN 
</P>
