assault her. 
</P>
<P>
 At his arraignment last week, Raymond Gerber Jr., 42, a patrol officer in the 
Harbor Division, pleaded innocent to three felony charges stemming from the 
Jan. 9 incident. 
</P>
<P>
 The 12-year Police Department veteran was arrested at his home Jan. 13 on 
suspicion of attacking a 33-year-old woman in the 200 block of West 7th Street 
in San Pedro, said Suzanne Childs, spokeswoman for the district attorney's 
office. 
</P>
<P>
 Police traced Gerber through the woman's description of her assailant's car. 
The assailant was not wearing a police uniform nor driving a patrol car. 
</P>
