<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY TOP 10 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The following are the top music sales in Orange County for the week of Jan. 16 
as compiled by SoundScan Inc. Data is from retailers' sales. The bottom chart 
rotates weekly. Albums 04,05,58,06,08 Last week Nation 1. "Music Box," Mariah 
Carey 2 13 2. "MTV Unplugged," 10,000 Maniacs 2 13 3. "Vs.," Pearl Jam 1 3 4. 
"Siamese Dream," Smashing Pumpkins 4 18 5. "Doggystyle," Snoop Doggy Dogg 5 2 
6. "Everybody Else Is Doing It, So ... ," The Cranberries 6 20 7. "So Far So 
Good," Bryan Adams 7 6 8. "The Colour of My Love," Celine Dion 19 23 9. 
"Greatest Hits," Tom Petty & The Heartbreakers 8 9 10. "In Utero," Nirvana 10 
25 Singles 04,05,54,06,08 Last week Nation 1. "All For Love," Bryan Adams, Rod 
