NEW ARREST IN SKATING ATTACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tonya Harding's former husband was arrested and charged Wednesday with 
financing and plotting the attack on rival Olympic figure skater Nancy 
Kerrigan. Harding was not charged, but one confessed accomplice, relying on 
secondhand information, implicated her. 
</P>
