<P>
 * I guess it's true what they say about tragedies happening in threes: 1) the 
L.A. riots, 2) the Southern California inferno, and 3) the Northridge 
earthquake! Does this mean we'll get a breather? 
</P>
<P>
 CLARENCE BROWN 
</P>
<P>
 Diamond Bar 
